Babacan Says Central Bank Decision Was Right, Milliyet Reports

-- B y   S t e v e   B r y a n t
-- 
2011-03-28T05:37:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/babacan-says-central-bank-decision-was-right-milliyet-reports.html
Turkey ’s central bank was right to
increase the required reserves banks must set aside against
liabilities, Deputy Prime Minister  Ali Babacan  said, according
to Milliyet newspaper.  While the bank’s decision may have surprised some banks and
economists, it was "timely and accurate" and there was a need
for additional steps to slow credit growth, Babacan said in
Istanbul, according to the newspaper.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
